            <p eId="annex_2_p_7"><b>Annex B – Hansard References</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>21 </num>
              <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act’s passage through Parliament.</p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="2.1in 2.1in 2.1in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Stage</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Date</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Hansard Reference</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Commons</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>21 June 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/bills/cbill/58-02/0083/210083.pdf"><u>Bill as introduced</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
